headline: Tyler Technologies Supports Delaware Department of Safety and Homeland Security’s Transition to NERIS for Federal Compliance
summary: PLANO, Texas, June 24, 2025--Tyler Technologies announced an agreement with the State of Delaware to move to the National Emergency Response Information System (NERIS).
